reviews.text: Overrated, for the wait, was the last table on line.  Staff would cut the line and keeping an eye on that, making sure no others sneak in.   Fluffy texture pancakes and delivered the standardized taste.  Drinks just like everywhere else that can be found.  Nice quick stop for sweet tooth friends get together, if don't have to wait for the line.  Staff being friendly and served efficiently.

We were able to grab a seat as soon as we arrived as there was no queue yet (went there around 7:30 or so. When we left, the queue was already long at around 8:30). The souffle pancake was just okay, though for me it just really tasted like eggs more than anything. Pizza’s a pass, it was nothing special it almost felt like I was just eating bread slathered with tomato sauce and cheese. Service was okay. They will give you a seat and give you the menu but you still have to order the food and pay for it at the counter.

The pancakes are so fluffy and delicious. One portion is pretty big, there’s 3 pancakes. Great for sharing but there’s a minimum order per person. Each person much order one item. 

There’s usually a small weigh but people come and go pretty quick.

Was recommended by a few friends.

Went at lunchtime on a Tuesday, didn't wait too long to get a table. I've been to go on a weekday during the day to avoid queuing long.

The pancakes were made fresh and was amazing. Bought 2 pancakes and 1 green tea latte. It is required that each person orders one item. And 1 portion of pancake is definitely enough.

Price wise, I was happy to pay as it was delicious an staff was friendly and spoke english.
Tasty pancakes,  but usually need to wait for at least an hour after ordering. Better go at 11am.

reviews.text:
#cassiegocwb
-
瘦編每次去希慎廣場都好想食Flipper’s，但每次都見條隊好長，唔想排。今次見到條隊唔係好長，終於都有機會試下。😋
-
瘦編就揀左期間限定嘅夕張密瓜斑戟，個斑戟真係好Soft，好似食緊空氣咁。個日本密瓜都好甜，配埋啲cream，好好食。另外再加左個外賣嘅綠茶班戟批，口感就一般，依個唔係新鮮整好，普通綠茶tart一個。🙆🏻‍♀️
-
終於都明點解次次都咁多人等位啦，因為佢上菜真係有啲耐，等超過15分鐘先有得食，所以翻枱時間要好耐。
-
味道評分▶️🌕🌕🌕🌗🌑 (3.5)
抵食評分▶️️🌕🌕🌗🌑🌑 (2.5)
回購評分▶️️️🌕🌕🌗🌑🌑 (2.5)
-

Fluffy texture pancakes and delivered the standardized taste.  Drinks just like everywhere else that can be found.  Nice quick stop for sweet tooth friends get together, if don't have to wait for the line.  Staff being friendly and served efficiently.

We were able to grab a seat as soon as we arrived as there was no queue yet (went there around 7:30 or so. When we left, the queue was already long at around 8:30). The souffle pancake was just okay, though for me it just really tasted like eggs more than anything. Pizza’s a pass, it was nothing special it almost felt like I was just eating bread slathered with tomato sauce and cheese. Service was okay. They will give you a seat and give you the menu but you still have to order the food and pay for it at the counter.

Flipper’s Hong Kong 開店超過一年了，
但還是不倒的排隊熱店，
當然是有他的厲害之處。
很多日系甜點店越洋開到香港，
都有機會因應各種因素保持不到水準，
而又因爲價位比原本國家的高，
很快就會讓香港人熱情冷卻。
但Flipper’s的熱潮從沒減退！
原因好簡單，keep得到品質，
也會定時跟日本店出限定菜單！
重點是還原度，水準跟日本店沒分別！
蛋香濃郁，空氣感pancake軟綿綿，
但不會過分的輕飄飄，配上酸甜新鮮的莓果，
甜度剛好，不膩不滯😌
加上一杯冰凍的Americano，
不就是一個美好的早上嘛☺️

不想排隊就開店時段去吧😋

The pancakes are so fluffy and delicious. One portion is pretty big, there’s 3 pancakes. Great for sharing but there’s a minimum order per person. Each person much order one item. 

There’s usually a small weigh but people come and go pretty quick.

reviews.text:
One of many malls dotting Causeway Bay area. Its lobby has a high vertical clearance. Trendy crowd...maybe because there was an Avengers exhibition going on at the time of my visit.

Had some difficulty finding Marketplace but as it turned out, was called Jasons, which is located two floors below ground.

The building had separate entries for the shopping areas and the office/residential area.
Amazing department store with all that you need in it. Great shops and restaurants
Large shopping mall in central location, not easy or pleasant to walk around or navigate. There are better malls in HK.

The big bookstore alone is worthy for a visit. The food court is decent and the general selection of stores is nicely put together. Directly connected to the mass transit too so this location is hard to beat.

Great shopping mall with can different kind of shops, including fashion, books store, restaurants, and Apple store.
Unlike other shopping mall, their escalator can easily reach each floor.
And there is a sky garden located on 4/F, which is a great place for relaxing, and it's open from 10am to 10pm
